foods.name: A generous loaf of artisan bread, freshly toasted to a perfect golden crisp. Smothered in a rich, herb-infused garlic butter and layered with a blend of melted mozzarella and parmesan cheeses. An irresistibly gooey and savory start to any meal.

foods.name: Rasmalai
foods.description: Rasmalai is a popular Indian dessert featuring soft, spongy paneer (cheese) discs or balls soaked in a sweetened, thickened, and flavored milk sauce, often infused with cardamom, saffron, and nuts like pistachios and almonds
